Package: fastEmbedR
Type: Package
Title: Fast Native UMAP and openTSNE from Precomputed KNN Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Stefano",
    family = "Caccia",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "tkcaccia@gmail.com")
Author: Stefano Caccia [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Stefano Caccia <tkcaccia@gmail.com>
Description: A compact UMAP and openTSNE-style implementation focused on fast
    embeddings from precomputed nearest-neighbor index and distance matrices.
    Nearest-neighbor search is provided by the companion faissR package, while
    fastEmbedR keeps preprocessing helpers, fixed-reference transform, and
    stochastic layout optimization in native code with explicit CPU/Metal/CUDA
    backend reporting.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/tkcaccia/fastEmbedR
BugReports: https://github.com/tkcaccia/fastEmbedR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
