    faissR,
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    float,
    igraph,
    jsonlite,
    knitr,
    leidenbase,
    rmarkdown,
    Rtsne,
    testthat
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++17, Fortran, Metal framework on macOS for optional embedding backends, CUDA toolkit for the optional CUDA embedding backend
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
